name: Fuji FinePix HS25EXR, 16MP Digita Camera, 30x Zoom, 3.0' LCD            APRIL
description: The Fuji FinePix HS25EXR 16MP Digital Camera offers versatility and optical quality to those photographers who don't want the lens-changing capability of a DSLR, but still want total control over their images. Equipped with advanced manual control, and a high performance 16MP EXR CMOS sensor, a whopping 30x optical zoom lens, 1080p Full HD Movie Mode, and a host of consumer friendly automatic settings, the HS25EXR is ready for anything from the simplest full-auto photo capture to the most advanced applications. The high-contrast (1:1100), high-resolution 3.0-inch LCD screen tilts to provide flexible viewing options for both high and low shooting positions and includes Sunlight Mode for clear viewing, even in bright outdoor conditions. The GUI (graphic user interface) incorporates flash technology, adding an intuitive and entertaining dimension to searching and displaying photos and accessing features. Plus a font display technology produces menus and icons that are easy on the eye.
short_description:
The Fuji FinePix HS25EXR 16MP Digital Camera offers versatility and optical quality to those photographers who don't want the lens-changing capability of a DSLR, but still want total control over their images. Equipped with advanced manual control, and a high performance 16MP EXR CMOS sensor, a whopping 30x optical zoom lens, 1080p Full HD Movie Mode, and a host of consumer friendly automatic settings, the HS25EXR is ready for anything from the simplest full-auto photo capture to the most advanced applications. The high-contrast (1:1100), high-resolution 3.0-inch LCD screen tilts to provide flexible viewing options for both high and low shooting positions and includes Sunlight Mode for clear viewing, even in bright outdoor conditions. The GUI (graphic user interface) incorporates flash technology, adding an intuitive and entertaining dimension to searching and displaying photos and accessing features. Plus a font display technology produces menus and icons that are easy on the eye.

  • 16.0 megapixel, 1/2-inch EXR CMOS sensor with primary color filter
  • Fujinon 30x optical zoom and digital zoom approx. 2x (up to approx. 60x, with 30x optical zoom)
  • Image Stabilization (CMOS Shift plus High ISO)
  • Electronic Viewfinder with Eye Sensor

  • Movie record button

  • High Speed Shooting Functions
  • Film Simulation Mode

  • Three Bracketing Functions: Film Simulatiion, Dynamic Range, AE
  • RAW shooting
  • Advanced shooting modes: Pro Focus Mode with Face Detection, Pro Low-light Mode
  • Multiple Exposures
  • Motion Panorama 360 degrees

  • Face Tracking Auto Focus, Face Detection, Face Recognition and Dog/Cat Detection
  • Approx. 25MB internal memory, SD/SDHC/SDXC memory card slot (card not included)
  • USB 2.0 High-Speed, HDMI mini connector, NTSC or PAL output with monaural sound

name: Canon EOS 5D MARK II EF 24-105 IS LENS KIT
description: The Canon 2764B004 EOS 5D Mark II Digital SLR Camera and EF 24-105 IS Lens Kit includes a the Mark II digital SLR camera that has a stunning 21.1-megapixel full-frame CMOS sensor with DIGIC 4 Image Processor, a vast ISO Range of 100-6400, plus EOS technologies like Auto Lighting Optimizer and Peripheral Illumination Correction. It supports Live View shooting, Live View HD videos, and more. It can shoot up to 3.9 fps, has 9 AF points plus 6 AF assist points, a new 98% coverage viewfinder, a 3.0-inch Clear View LCD (920,000 dots/VGA) and a rugged build. The EF 24-105 IS Lens is a standard zoom lens that can cover a large zoom area ranging from 24mm wide-angle to 105mm portrait-length telephoto. And its Image Stabilizer technology steadies camera shake up to three stops.
short_description:
The Canon 2764B004 EOS 5D Mark II Digital SLR Camera and EF 24-105 IS Lens Kit includes a the Mark II digital SLR camera that has a stunning 21.1-megapixel full-frame CMOS sensor with DIGIC 4 Image Processor, a vast ISO Range of 100-6400, plus EOS technologies like Auto Lighting Optimizer and Peripheral Illumination Correction. It supports Live View shooting, Live View HD videos, and more. It can shoot up to 3.9 fps, has 9 AF points plus 6 AF assist points, a new 98% coverage viewfinder, a 3.0-inch Clear View LCD (920,000 dots/VGA) and a rugged build. The EF 24-105 IS Lens is a standard zoom lens that can cover a large zoom area ranging from 24mm wide-angle to 105mm portrait-length telephoto. And its Image Stabilizer technology steadies camera shake up to three stops.

name: Canon EOS 7D Digita Camera - Body only with added lens 55-250mm (2044B002)
description: Canon 3814B004L1-KIT includes the EOS 7D 18MP Digital SLR Camera Body and EF-S 55-250mm f/4-5.6 IS Telephoto Zoom Lens. The EOS 7D Digital SLR Camera has many features including an 18MP APS-C size CMOS sensor, Dual DIGIC 4 Image Processors, and an all cross-type 19-point AF system with improved AI Servo II AF subject tracking and user-selectable AF area selection modes for sharp focus. The EOS 7D's Intelligent Viewfinder provides 100% coverage and displays user-selected AF modes as well as a spot metering circle. The EF-S 55-250mm f/4-5.6 IS Telephoto Zoom Lens is designed with Optical Image Stabilizer technology while retaining compactness and lightness. This high zoom ratio lens is equivalent to a focal length of 88-400mm in the 35mm format.

Plus, the EF 70-300mm f/4-5.6 IS USM Telephoto Zoom Lens has Image Stabilizer technology that provides up to three stops of ''shake'' correction, and the ''Mode 2'' option.

name: Canon EOS 60D with EF-S 18-135mm with added lens 55-250mm (2044B002)
description: The Canon 4460B004L1-KIT includes an EOS 60D Digital SLR Camera, EF-S 18-135mm f3.5-5.6 IS Lens and EF-S 55-250mm f/4-5.6 IS Telephoto Zoom Lens. This digital camera features an APS-C sized 18.0 megapixel CMOS sensor for tremendous images, a DIGIC 4 Image Processor for finer detail and excellent color reproduction. The Multi-control Dial enables users to operate menus and settings with a simple touch. It also features a vari-angle 3.0-inch Clear View LCD monitor. And covering a range from 29mm-216mm in 35mm format, the EF-S 18-135mm f/3.5-5.6 IS lens offers a winning combination of size, range and features and is a perfect complement to APS-C cameras. The EF-S 55-250mm f/4-5.6 IS Telephoto Zoom Lens is designed with Optical Image Stabilizer technology while retaining compactness and lightness. This high zoom ratio lens is equivalent to a focal length of 88-400mm in the 35mm format.
product_name: Canon EOS 60D with EF-S 18-135mm with added lens 55-250mm (2044B002)

name: Canon EOS 60D with EF-S 18-135mm with added lens 70-300mm (0345B002)
description: The Canon 4460B004L2-KIT includes an EOS 60D Digital SLR Camera, EF-S 18-135mm f3.5-5.6 IS Lens and an EF 70-300mm f/4-5.6 IS USM Telephoto Zoom Lens. This digital camera features an APS-C sized 18.0 megapixel CMOS sensor for tremendous images, a DIGIC 4 Image Processor for finer detail and excellent color reproduction. The Multi-control Dial enables users to operate menus and settings with a simple touch. It also features a vari-angle 3.0-inch Clear View LCD monitor. And covering a range from 29mm-216mm in 35mm format, the EF-S 18-135mm f/3.5-5.6 IS lens offers a winning combination of size, range and features and is a perfect complement to APS-C cameras. The EF 70-300mm f/4-5.6 IS USM Telephoto Zoom Lens has improved Image Stabilizer technology that provides up to three stops of ''shake'' correction, and the ''Mode 2'' option stabilizes images while panning with a moving subject.

The digital camera features an 18.0 Megapixel CMOS Image Sensor and increased light sensitivity for low light photography. It also has an advanced HD Movie mode for gorgeous Full HD movies. The EF-S 18-55mm IS Lens stabilization allows sharp hand-held shots at shutter speeds up to four stops slower than otherwise possible. The camera case is water resistant, with a padded interior to protect your camera and the 8GB memory card lets you archive and share your precious moments. Plus, the Mini HDMI Cable easily connects to a TV or projector to share your adventures in a clean 1080p picture.
